ount field alongside array data for frontend conditional r\",\"scope\":\"src/app/api/instructor/dashboard/route.ts\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Admin oversight UI uses a distinct 'Course Oversight' heading (not the instructor's 'Your Courses' heading) to differentiate the admin supervisory view from the instructor self-view.\",\"scope\":\"src/app/(frontend)/instructor-dashboard/InstructorDashboardContent.tsx\"},{\"kind\":\"decision\",\"text\":\"The server-side pattern builds an `instructorsByCourse` map from `courses` + `course-instructors` collections, then injects the per-course instructor array into each course object before returning — a\",\"scope\":\"src/app/api/instructor/dashboard/route.ts\"},{\"kind\":\"gotcha\",\"text\":\"The InstructorDashboardContent component conditionally renders the admin 'Course Oversigh","createdAt":"2026-04-19T15:42:54.026Z","wordCount":1000,"positions":[2,10,18,31,38,47,59,73,86,96,105,120,123,131,151,159,167,178,185,195,201,207,217,223,232,241,257,265,269,273,277,288,298,304,311,318,331,338,344,354,357,364,374,381,392,401,409,423,428,437,449,467,473,485,499,510,515,523,531,535,540,550,561,571,598,606,613,624,635,642,647,655,666,687,697,709,716,729,747,759,763,770,781,787,797,804,811,818,834,842,846,850,854,865,875,881,888,895,904,915,942,952,966,978,985,992]},"ep_stage_diary_002":{"taskId":"2","episodeId":"ep_stage_diary_002","source":"stage_diary","content":"{\"stage\":\"review\",\"insights\":[{\"kind\":\"gotcha\",\"text\":\"When reorganizing roles (e.g., moving them to a new module), update all backward-compat re-export files too — it's easy to forget them.\",\"scope\":\"src/server/payload/collections/Users/roles.ts\"},{\"kind\":\"gotcha\",\"text\":\"Backend-integration layers that import roles from shared infra need their import paths updated when roles are reorganized.\",\"scope\":\"src/server/payload/backend-integration\"},{\"kind\":\"lesson\",\"text\":\"Always confirm the implementation branch is up to date with or